{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-post-js","path":"/posts/ski7c42oox4zzfst/","result":{"data":{"sitePage":null},"pageContext":{"url":"posts/ski7c42oox4zzfst","relativePath":"posts/ski7c42oox4zzfst","frontmatter":{"title":"A Dream: What is Brickverse?","stackbit_url_path":"posts/ski7c42oox4zzfst","date":"2023-02-11T23:00:23","excerpt":"","tags":[],"categories":[],"template":"post"},"html":"<p>Yesterday I had a strange but interesting dream. In the dream, I became another man which I am opposite in the real life. In the dream I became two parts, one is an observer and the other is an actor.</p>\n<p>A man in the dream asked: What is <strong>Brickverse</strong>? Then the actor of me stood out and shout like Shen Yulin: Even in the metaverse, there are bricks we can play!<span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 590px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/793e53cbf8bfe896fbf5684287e1f0b1/5a190/1676186845145-4edd7061-b0ca-446d-84bd-dc5f5805bc8d.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 100%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block; transition: opacity 0.5s 0.5s; pointer-events: none;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"image.png\"\n        title=\"image.png\"\n        src=\"/static/793e53cbf8bfe896fbf5684287e1f0b1/fcda8/1676186845145-4edd7061-b0ca-446d-84bd-dc5f5805bc8d.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/793e53cbf8bfe896fbf5684287e1f0b1/12f09/1676186845145-4edd7061-b0ca-446d-84bd-dc5f5805bc8d.png 148w,\n/static/793e53cbf8bfe896fbf5684287e1f0b1/e4a3f/1676186845145-4edd7061-b0ca-446d-84bd-dc5f5805bc8d.png 295w,\n/static/793e53cbf8bfe896fbf5684287e1f0b1/fcda8/1676186845145-4edd7061-b0ca-446d-84bd-dc5f5805bc8d.png 590w,\n/static/793e53cbf8bfe896fbf5684287e1f0b1/5a190/1676186845145-4edd7061-b0ca-446d-84bd-dc5f5805bc8d.png 800w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 590px) 100vw, 590px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;opacity:0;transition:opacity 0.5s;color:inherit;box-shadow:inset 0px 0px 0px 400px white;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span><br />What is its use anyway?</p>\n<p>The actor of mine answered with passion: Well, <strong>use is the least useful thing here in the Brickverse, and useless is most we treasure here</strong>.</p>\n<p>When I came back to life, I laughed at my crazy actor of me. But I do see many strangers joining the <strong>Brickverse</strong> space, I think I need to give them some introduction to the <strong>Brickverse</strong>.<br /><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 590px; \"\n    >\n      <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 75%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block; transition: opacity 0.5s 0.5s; pointer-events: none;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"image.png\"\n        title=\"image.png\"\n        src=\"/static/df91a5af66f37da294eb1d5112c27721/fcda8/1676187290913-5a630334-7360-48d0-b015-261555434d9d.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/df91a5af66f37da294eb1d5112c27721/12f09/1676187290913-5a630334-7360-48d0-b015-261555434d9d.png 148w,\n/static/df91a5af66f37da294eb1d5112c27721/e4a3f/1676187290913-5a630334-7360-48d0-b015-261555434d9d.png 295w,\n/static/df91a5af66f37da294eb1d5112c27721/fcda8/1676187290913-5a630334-7360-48d0-b015-261555434d9d.png 590w,\n/static/df91a5af66f37da294eb1d5112c27721/efc66/1676187290913-5a630334-7360-48d0-b015-261555434d9d.png 885w,\n/static/df91a5af66f37da294eb1d5112c27721/c83ae/1676187290913-5a630334-7360-48d0-b015-261555434d9d.png 1180w,\n/static/df91a5af66f37da294eb1d5112c27721/c6720/1676187290913-5a630334-7360-48d0-b015-261555434d9d.png 1922w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 590px) 100vw, 590px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;opacity:0;transition:opacity 0.5s;color:inherit;box-shadow:inset 0px 0px 0px 400px white;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n    </span>\n<a name=kd2oD></a></p>\n<h1>Unknown is attractive</h1>\n<p>I dont know what <strong>Brickverse</strong> is, either. I just played with it, and some other guys are playing in it, too.</p>\n<p>We are constructing the <strong>Brickverse</strong> now, but not sure where can it go. Its hard to foresee the future, but we are enjoying the moment now.</p>\n<p><a name=OXndr></a></p>\n<h1>The only rule is no rule at all</h1>\n<p>We have no rules here, and just welcome anyone to join.</p>\n<p><a name=pHVvk></a></p>\n<h1>As is</h1>\n<p><a name=i8SFn></a></p>\n<h2>Main sites</h2>\n<p>Now we are doing web, but in the future, we may have apps, mini-programs, etc, given enough resources.\n<a name=OF8oL></a></p>\n<h3>Public Domains</h3>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"https://brickverse.net\">https://brickverse.net</a> is our main entry point</li>\n<li>We also have a shorter alternative domain: <a href=\"https://brick.cat\">https://brick.cat</a></li>\n</ul>\n<p><a name=v3PH3></a></p>\n<h3>Workforce sites</h3>\n<p><a name=Z72ux></a></p>\n<h4>GitHub</h4>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/brick-verse\">https://github.com/brick-verse</a></li>\n<li>We are using GitHub actions to deploy our sites automatically. We have several reports there but only a few are open-source right now. Hopefully, well public more in the future.</li>\n</ul>\n<p><a name=ElFB6></a></p>\n<h4>JIRA</h4>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"https://brickverse.atlassian.net\">https://brickverse.atlassian.net</a></li>\n<li>We have a JIRA site to manage our tasks and a kanban board. But currently, we are using the free version, so only 10 members can join the workspace and now its full.</li>\n</ul>\n<p><a name=hVRsD></a></p>\n<h4>Slack channel</h4>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"https://brickverse.slack.com\">https://brickverse.slack.com</a></li>\n<li>For communications. But currently, most of the messages are generated by JIRA bots.</li>\n</ul>\n<p><a name=HasYl></a></p>\n<h2>Infrastructures</h2>\n<p>We are using free infrastructures mainly but also a few paid ones.\n<a name=bqu9a></a></p>\n<h3>Cloudflare</h3>\n<p>For hosting the domain brickverse.net\n<a name=v0bF9></a></p>\n<h3>Vercel</h3>\n<p>For hosting the shorter domain brick.cat and our front-end apps.<br /><a href=\"https://vercel.com/brickverse\">https://vercel.com/brickverse</a><br /><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 590px; \"\n    >\n      <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 78.37837837837837%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block; transition: opacity 0.5s 0.5s; pointer-events: none;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"image.png\"\n        title=\"image.png\"\n        src=\"/static/cb14439e97fc1b58b618d8957ee1abae/fcda8/1676186960957-8f8b1d10-226f-4ac3-b18d-e00b1373e55b.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/cb14439e97fc1b58b618d8957ee1abae/12f09/1676186960957-8f8b1d10-226f-4ac3-b18d-e00b1373e55b.png 148w,\n/static/cb14439e97fc1b58b618d8957ee1abae/e4a3f/1676186960957-8f8b1d10-226f-4ac3-b18d-e00b1373e55b.png 295w,\n/static/cb14439e97fc1b58b618d8957ee1abae/fcda8/1676186960957-8f8b1d10-226f-4ac3-b18d-e00b1373e55b.png 590w,\n/static/cb14439e97fc1b58b618d8957ee1abae/efc66/1676186960957-8f8b1d10-226f-4ac3-b18d-e00b1373e55b.png 885w,\n/static/cb14439e97fc1b58b618d8957ee1abae/c83ae/1676186960957-8f8b1d10-226f-4ac3-b18d-e00b1373e55b.png 1180w,\n/static/cb14439e97fc1b58b618d8957ee1abae/c6720/1676186960957-8f8b1d10-226f-4ac3-b18d-e00b1373e55b.png 1922w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 590px) 100vw, 590px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;opacity:0;transition:opacity 0.5s;color:inherit;box-shadow:inset 0px 0px 0px 400px white;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n    </span>\n<a name=oxtJg></a></p>\n<h3>Okteto</h3>\n<p><a name=VtAT4></a></p>\n<h3>Filess</h3>\n<p><a name=N7e8R></a></p>\n<h3>nhost</h3>\n<p>...</p>\n<p><a name=laNDg></a></p>\n<h1>We are NOT</h1>\n<p>Just now I did a search and found there is a **youtube channel **named also <strong>Brickverse</strong>, but they are not us and we are not them. We have something in common, though. LOL</p>","pages":[],"site":{"siteMetadata":{"title":"Jeff Tian","author":"@zizhujy","description":"A wild full stack developer","palette":"yellow","header":{"title":"Jeff Tian","tagline":"A wild developer","logo_img":"https://images.ctfassets.net/qixg1o8tujmf/7z1ua3nTOC5B7DwwzAki8I/4e1a05f8db770c285a492eeb1eaa398f/imageedit_3_2509022194.png","background_img":"https://images.ctfassets.net/qixg1o8tujmf/7m0jrKYaDBwEvlc5lo8nt6/6d50a5050d9cdc0d4d2047e35feac292/10648733_696750647079056_2800539603462658695_o.jpg","has_nav":true,"nav_links":[{"label":"Home","url":"/","style":"link","type":"action"},{"label":"About","url":"/about","style":"link","type":"action"},{"label":"关于","url":"https://ggyy.pa-pa.me/about","style":"link","icon_class":"lorem-ipsum","new_window":true,"type":"action"},{"label":"Contact","url":"/contact","style":"link","type":"action"},{"label":"Support Me","url":"/support-me","style":"link","type":"action"},{"label":"叽叽歪歪","url":"https://ggyy.pa-pa.me/","style":"link","icon_class":"lorem-ipsum","new_window":true,"type":"action"}],"has_social":true,"social_links":[{"label"